init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are now the queen bee, and you must guide your bee-clan to the safety of a nearby flower.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And you have no idea why all these bees are following you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Because "Humans have been oppressing bees for so long, now it's time for bees to dominant over humans."

actions.name: text-delete
